Gluten is a protein found in wheat, barley and rye. Those who react to wheat will enjoy this recipe. Ingredients Preparation Step 1 Mix the mashed banana, eggs, olive oil, honey, and vanilla extract in a large bowl. Step 2 Add in the oat flour, oats, baking powder, and blueberries and combine. Step 3 Line your muffin tins and scoop the batter into each muffin liner. Step 4 Bake at 180 degrees C for about 20-25 minutes or until a toothpick comes out clean. Step Remove from the oven and cool, before storing in an air-tight container. Enjoy with friends and family.